-- FriendFinder Offers $210 Million for Playboy Enterprises
-- Bill Koenig
-- 2010-07-15T15:35:48Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-15/penthouse-owner-offers-210-million-for-hugh-hefner-s-playboy-enterprises.html

          
          
             FriendFinder Networks Inc. said it
has made a proposal to acquire Playboy Enterprises Inc. for $210
million.  
 The information was disclosed in an e-mailed statement.  
          
          


  


        